{"tid":1757297,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「覺醒要由情理走向民生政治」","createTime":"2019-11-26T12:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T12:45:21.000Z","uid":65139,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a650856afc408d04afd4da82f19b008673dc3323","tid":1757297,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:33:22.000Z","msg":"幾個月嘅高壓令冷感香港人由警暴中「警」醒覺悟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但警暴只係由情感同理惻隱之心角度「（刀）切」入香港人生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而一般香港人其實仍然對政治認知同埋熱情尚淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n單靠警暴激發起嘅主動性同復仇心態難以唯持到下年，下下年...呢團火好快被舒適嘅生活同冬天吹熄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要香港人真正覺醒之路仍遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要真正做到「政治乃眾人的事」<br />\n必須要令生活融入政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民要明白政客一言一行同決定都會影響生活<br />\n政府任何一個提議都足以製造更嚴重嘅革命<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">空穴來風 蝴蝶效應不止</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如呢兩單<br />\n「居中國內地香港人投票機制」<br />\n「檢討檢討檢討委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每一步港共諗嘅 講嘅 行嘅都足以摧殘香港</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要香港人全民皆政<br />\n前日算係民選嘅區議會只係一小步咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多野可以做，要繼續做<br />\n<br />\n例如文宣轉陣<br />\n要藉民憤未平，將市民嘅主動性帶入更多有用資訊，理性分析政局，同時不忘用體制內方法抗衡垃圾港共。<br />\n<br />\n同時小市民參政，除咗心仲要身體要力行<br />\n要靠大家同連登仔將<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">online嘅野走到offline，已經offline嘅野加大到sunshine<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n由落手落腳做地區義工到平時參與社區活動等等<br />\n<br />\n香港人繼續努力<br />\n連登仔都繼續給力唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c11295a323cfa6c39ef5f8222ac451d7852ff6a","tid":1757297,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:34:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad1575206fb74d96882cf9c2b3b25068111dc896","tid":1757297,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9f49e98faa67d04fab5f8169ea4f5e6393381573","tid":1757297,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:36:04.000Z","msg":"雖然知無咁快，但好期待有呢一日"},{"pid":"b9c4eeefff38c87d6f5f0ca4f9b699ee6a416087","tid":1757297,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:36:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e59212b54cd42d7747b0183f3ec18d3bbba95af9","tid":1757297,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:45:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}